    "title": "Senior Fleet Manager at KTC Logistics",
    "description": "KTC Logistics invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Fleet Manager at our Surat location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout KTC Logistics:\nKTC Logistics is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in WMS\n• Proficiency in Vendor Management\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Flexible working hours\n• Referral bonus program\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with KTC Logistics!",
